<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>577</hymn_number>
<author>W.H. Doane</author>
<title>Jeso Sakaizanay FFPM577</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jeso Sakaizanay,
 Sakaiza rahateo !
 Indreto izahay, vonjeo,
 Fa be ny adinay :
 Jeso, Sakaizanay,
 Sakaiza rahateo !
 Indreto izahay, vonjeo,
 Fa be ny adinay.

[V2]
 Jeso Sakaizanay,
 Sakaiza be fitia !
 Tariho izahay hanao
 Ny zava-tianao :
 Jeso, Sakaizanay, ..sns.

[V3]
 Jeso Sakaizanay,
 Sakaiza tsy mandao !
 Na dia mpanota aza re
 Izahay mpanomponao :
 Jeso, Sakaizanay, ..sns.

[V4]
 Jeso Sakaizanay,
 Sakaiza tsy mamoy,
 Na ory na finaritra
 Izahay ankehitrio :
 Jeso, Sakaizanay, ..sns.

[V5]
 Jeso Sakaizanay,
 Omaly sy anio,
 Ka mbola ho Sakaizanay
 Mandrakizay doria :
 Jeso, Sakaizanay, ..sns.</lyrics>
</song>